{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_0191gnXkrFZrCCk78gTYFmj6","type":"tool_result","content":"/workspace/docs/workflows.md:    agent_command = \"claude\"\n/workspace/docs/workflows.md:    agent_command = \"claude\"\n/workspace/docs/workflows.md:    agent_command = \"claude\"\n/workspace/docs/workflows.md:var > default `claude`.\n/workspace/docs/workflows.md:    agent_command = \"claude\"\n/workspace/docs/USAGE.md:| `agent_command` | string | Agent binary name(s), comma-separated for fallback chains, e.g. `\"claude,gemini\"`. |\n/workspace/docs/USAGE.md:    agent_command = \"gemini\"\n/workspace/docs/USAGE.md:    agent_command = \"claude\"\n/workspace/docs/USAGE.md:4. Default: `claude`\n/workspace/docs/USAGE.md:agent_command = \"claude,gemini,codex\"\n/workspace/docs/USAGE.md:Known agents (e.g. `claude`) get default arguments (`-p --output-format stream-json --verbose --dangerously-skip-permissions`). Unknown agents receive the prompt on stdin with no flags. Override with `agent_args`.\n/workspace/docs/USAGE.md:    agent_command = \"claude\"\n/workspace/docs/USAGE.md:- **Auth mounts**: `~/.claude` and `~/.claude.json` are bind-mounted read-only for Claude Code session reuse.\n/workspace/docs/USAGE.md:- Your project's build dependencies and the agent binary (e.g. `claude`)\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-cloche-base-docker-design.md:**Not included:** Node.js, npm, claude-code, language runtimes, build tools. These are\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-cloche-base-docker-design.md:RUN npm install -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-cloche-base-docker-design.md:#   RUN npm install -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-cloche-base-docker-design.md:| `Dockerfile` (root / cloche project) | Simplify to `FROM cloche-base:latest` + add claude-code |\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-20-cloche-implementation.md:mkdir -p internal/adapters/agents/claudecode\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-20-cloche-implementation.md:\t// Name returns the adapter identifier (e.g., \"claudecode\", \"generic\").\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-23-cloche-init.md:RUN npm install -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-23-cloche-init-design.md:installs git and claude-code, creates `agent` user.\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-23-cloche-init-design.md:RUN npm install -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-20-cloche-system-design.md:    claudecode/  # AgentAdapter for Claude Code\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-20-cloche-system-design.md:  interface. Claude Code adapter knows how to invoke `claude` CLI. Generic adapter runs\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md:adapter — shell out to a command (e.g., `claude -p`).","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_017xCxwq7vtimYnzVCvKMfnj","session_id":"aeb114c6-22ff-4078-baec-d21a69457fa7","uuid":"7f059e3c-c0fb-493c-b97b-16e764b74e53"}
